    <td width=64%><font face=Verdana size=2>What else have we been doing 
    you ask?  Well, we dropped the Creator a couple of days ago.  He 
    dropped a Silver Trinket of Speed for Dryzlil and a Blacksmithing Hammer for 
    Nuvian.</font><p align=center>
    <img border=0 src=images/news/13April02/EmpSsrahoho.gif width=351 height=91></p>
    <p><font face=Verdana size=2>Also dropped Blood... grats Serrath on the 
    mace and Kastrina on the 11 int 25 hp / mana and some saves earring (yes, 
    I'm serious).  Decided to throw ourselves at the Emperor and got him to 
    80% (which actually means 93%)... *shrug* it was something to do. ;)</font></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p><font face=Verdana size=2>Unfortunately for our members our time in Ssra 
is drawing to a close.  I know most of us are crying (tears of joy) at the 
thought of leaving Ssra but I'm sure we will be back soon enough, don't worry!</font></p>
<p><font face=Verdana size=2>That just about draws my update to a close.  
I really don't know what to say at the moment... so I'll just let my quotes do 
the talking for me!  Oh, /hug Povar... I lub joo all - really!  I hope 
you guys saw the humor in my update, really it's all in good fun. :p  LoL</font></p>
